<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<kml xmlns="http://www.opengis.net/kml/2.2">
<Document>
  <name>澳大利亚自驾路线 2026五一</name>
  <description>大洋路 × 菲利普岛 × 塔斯马尼亚 | 2026年4月25日–5月5日 | 两人情侣</description>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       颜色样式定义
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->

  <!-- 大洋路：橙色 -->
  <Style id="s-gor-line">
    <LineStyle><color>ff0098ff</color><width>5</width></LineStyle>
  </Style>
  <!-- 内陆返程：橙色半透明 -->
  <Style id="s-inland-line">
    <LineStyle><color>660098ff</color><width>3</width></LineStyle>
  </Style>
  <!-- 菲利普岛：紫色 -->
  <Style id="s-phi-line">
    <LineStyle><color>ffb0279c</color><width>5</width></LineStyle>
  </Style>
  <!-- 飞行段：红色 -->
  <Style id="s-flight-line">
    <LineStyle><color>ff2828c6</color><width>3</width></LineStyle>
  </Style>
  <!-- 塔斯马尼亚主路：绿色 -->
  <Style id="s-tas-line">
    <LineStyle><color>ff006900</color><width>5</width></LineStyle>
  </Style>
  <!-- 塔斯马尼亚返程：绿色半透明 -->
  <Style id="s-tas-return-line">
    <LineStyle><color>66006900</color><width>3</width></LineStyle>
  </Style>

  <!-- 标注点样式 -->
  <Style id="s-airport">
    <IconStyle>
      <scale>1.3</scale>
      <Icon><href>https://maps.google.com/mapfiles/ms/icons/blue-dot.png</href></Icon>
    </IconStyle>
  </Style>
  <Style id="s-star">
    <IconStyle>
      <scale>1.4</scale>
      <Icon><href>https://maps.google.com/mapfiles/ms/icons/red-dot.png</href></Icon>
    </IconStyle>
  </Style>
  <Style id="s-orange">
    <IconStyle>
      <scale>1.1</scale>
      <Icon><href>https://maps.google.com/mapfiles/ms/icons/orange-dot.png</href></Icon>
    </IconStyle>
  </Style>
  <Style id="s-purple">
    <IconStyle>
      <scale>1.1</scale>
      <Icon><href>https://maps.google.com/mapfiles/ms/icons/purple-dot.png</href></Icon>
    </IconStyle>
  </Style>
  <Style id="s-green">
    <IconStyle>
      <scale>1.1</scale>
      <Icon><href>https://maps.google.com/mapfiles/ms/icons/green-dot.png</href></Icon>
    </IconStyle>
  </Style>
  <Style id="s-yellow">
    <IconStyle>
      <scale>1.0</scale>
      <Icon><href>https://maps.google.com/mapfiles/ms/icons/yellow-dot.png</href></Icon>
    </IconStyle>
  </Style>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       第一章：维多利亚州（大洋路 + 菲利普岛）
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <Folder>
    <name>第一章：维多利亚州 Day2–5</name>
    <description>大洋路 + 菲利普岛。Day2取车，Day3大洋路全天，Day4企鹅岛，Day5还车飞塔斯马尼亚。</description>

    <!-- 停留点 -->
    <Placemark>
      <name>✈ 墨尔本（Day2 取车·住）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>抵达+休整日</b><br>
取租车（Hertz/Avis，MEL国际航站楼）<br>
下午：联邦广场·弗林德斯街站·Flat White咖啡<br>
⚠️ <b>明天05:30出发，务必早睡！</b><br><br>
住宿：Mantra on Russell / Holiday Inn Central<br>
AUD 150–250/晚]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-airport</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>144.9631,-37.8136,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>托尔博 大洋路起点（Day3）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[大洋路正式起点，标志性纪念拱门。<br>
冲浪圣地，Rip Curl与Quicksilver发源地。<br>
停留约15分钟，拍完出发。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-orange</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>144.3244,-38.3313,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>安格尔西 野生袋鼠高尔夫球场（Day3 可选）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[Anglesea Golf Club草坪上常年有约300只野生袋鼠！<br>
购票进场约AUD12.5/人，停留30分钟。<br>
<i>时间紧可跳过，肯内特河考拉更值得</i>]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-yellow</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>144.1874,-38.4059,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>⭐ 肯内特河 路边野生考拉（Day3）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>全程最值得停的考拉点！</b><br>
沿Grey River Road路边桉树上免费看野生考拉。<br>
完全免费·距离极近·无需门票·胜过任何动物园<br>
建议停留30分钟仔细寻找（看树叉处）。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-star</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>143.8414,-38.6591,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>阿波罗湾 午餐+⛽加满油（Day3）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>⚠️ 必须在此加满油！这是最后可靠的加油站。</b><br>
Apollo Bay Fishermen's Co-op：码头直销龙虾·鲍鱼·鱼排<br>
AUD 30–60/份，停留约1小时。<br>
FoodWorks/IGA超市买好食物和水（往后无大型超市）]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-orange</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>143.6726,-38.7605,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>洛克阿德峡谷（Day3）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[1878年沉船命名。深红悬崖+碧绿海水+白沙滩。<br>
推荐：Island Archway + Blowhole两条短线<br>
免费，停留1–1.5小时。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-orange</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>143.0218,-38.6870,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>吉布森石阶（Day3）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[走下石阶到海滩，仰视独立石柱Gog和Magog。<br>
免费，约20分钟。涨潮时可能关闭。<br>
紧邻十二门徒停车场，不要错过！]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-orange</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>142.9876,-38.6649,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>⭐⭐⭐ 十二门徒 日落（Day3 16:30前到）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>大洋路压轴之作！</b><br>
5月日落约17:15，建议16:30前抵达占好观景台位置。<br>
免费入场，有地下通道连接两处主观景台。<br><br>
<b>✈ 直升机升级</b>（强烈推荐！）：<br>
16分钟 AUD 195/人（两人合计AUD 390）<br>
预约：12apostleshelicopters.com.au<br>
⚠️ 大风天气可能取消，需确认天气]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-star</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>142.9958,-38.6596,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>群岛湾 Bay of Islands（Day3 延伸）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[距十二门徒约10km西行，灰白石灰岩柱群错落大海。<br>
视野比十二门徒更开阔，<b>几乎没有中国游客</b>。<br>
免费，时间允许强烈建议顺路看。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-yellow</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>142.8744,-38.5803,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🏨 坎贝尔港住宿（Day3晚）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>住宿：Southern Ocean Motor Inn</b><br>
或 Daysy Hill Country Cottages（网红田园小屋）<br>
紧邻十二门徒，可听浪声入眠。<br>
AUD 130–220/晚]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-green</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>142.9957,-38.6127,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🐋 沃南布尔 5月观鲸台（可选延伸）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>5月专属体验！夏季旺季完全没有此机会。</b><br>
Logan's Beach专设观鲸台，免费看南露脊鲸育幼·喷水。<br>
距坎贝尔港约62km，可在此住一晚再走内陆路返程。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-yellow</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>142.4851,-38.3837,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🐨 菲利普岛考拉保育中心（Day4）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[木栈道与树冠等高，近距离平视野生考拉。<br>
AUD 15/人，停留约45分钟。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-purple</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>145.1583,-38.4833,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🦭 诺比斯角 海豹礁（Day4）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[Seal Rocks数千只毛海豹栖息礁石，南半球最大聚集地之一。<br>
免费，建议带望远镜。旁边南极体验馆AUD 15/人。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-purple</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>144.8667,-38.5167,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>⭐⭐⭐ 小蓝企鹅归巢 Penguin Parade（Day4 ~19:30）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>全程最治愈的记忆！</b><br>
体长仅33cm的小蓝企鹅每晚从大海归来，摇摇摆摆爬上岸。<br>
约19:30开始（日落后），持续约1小时。<br><br>
票价：AUD 30–35/人（标准票）<br>
升级：地下视角台 AUD 40–60/人<br>
预约：<b>penguins.org.au</b><br>
⚠️ <b>绝对禁止使用任何闪光灯！</b>]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-star</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>144.9069,-38.5182,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🏨 菲利普岛住宿（Day4晚）</name>
      <description><![CDATA[住宿：Ramada Phillip Island Nature Resort<br>
或 The Island Accommodation<br>
企鹅归巢区步行可达。AUD 150–280/晚<br>
次日早上轻松返回墨尔本，避免深夜疲劳驾驶。]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#s-purple</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>145.2335,-38.4522,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>

    <!-- 路线 -->
    <Placemark>
      <name>🟠 大洋路驾车路线（Day3）</name>
      <description>墨尔本→托尔博→安格尔西→肯内特河→阿波罗湾→洛克阿德峡谷→十二门徒→坎贝尔港 | 约340km，05:30出发</description>
      <styleUrl>#s-gor-line</styleUrl>
      <LineString>
        <tessellate>1</tessellate>
        <coordinates>
          144.9631,-37.8136,0
          144.7000,-37.9200,0
          144.5000,-38.0500,0
          144.3500,-38.1500,0
          144.3244,-38.3313,0
          144.1874,-38.4059,0
          144.0500,-38.4800,0
          143.9839,-38.5442,0
          143.8800,-38.6100,0
          143.8414,-38.6591,0
          143.7500,-38.7100,0
          143.6726,-38.7605,0
          143.5127,-38.8591,0
          143.4500,-38.8400,0
          143.3969,-38.7891,0
          143.2500,-38.7200,0
          143.1000,-38.6800,0
          143.0218,-38.6870,0
          142.9876,-38.6649,0
          142.9958,-38.6596,0
          142.9957,-38.6127,0
        </coordinates>
      </LineString>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🟠 内陆返程（Day4，Princes Hwy）</name>
      <description>坎贝尔港→内陆路→墨尔本，约3小时，沿途在小镇喝咖啡</description>
      <styleUrl>#s-inland-line</styleUrl>
      <LineString>
        <tessellate>1</tessellate>
        <coordinates>
          142.9957,-38.6127,0
          143.2000,-38.4000,0
          143.5884,-38.3384,0
          143.9000,-38.2000,0
          144.2000,-38.1000,0
          144.3500,-38.1500,0
          144.6000,-37.9500,0
          144.9631,-37.8136,0
        </coordinates>
      </LineString>
    </Placemark>

    <Placemark>
      <name>🟣 菲利普岛路线（Day4）</name>
      <description>墨尔本→菲利普岛，约140km，1.5小时</description>
      <styleUrl>#s-phi-line</styleUrl>
      <LineString>
        <tessellate>1</tessellate>
        <coordinates>
          144.9631,-37.8136,0
          145.1500,-38.0000,0
          145.3000,-38.2000,0
